00:34:08.560 --> 00:34:11.990
world. You have it all by

00:34:12.000 --> 00:34:14.790
the tail.

00:34:14.800 --> 00:34:18.389
But you don't take time to thank God for

00:34:18.399 --> 00:34:20.389
what you do have, even if you're a

00:34:20.399 --> 00:34:23.109
multi-millionaire, because you become

00:34:23.119 --> 00:34:25.750
so accustomed to how you live. I'm

00:34:25.760 --> 00:34:28.550
trying to tell you, if you are

00:34:28.560 --> 00:34:30.790
going to make it in the days ahead,

00:34:30.800 --> 00:34:32.310
you've got to learn how to have a

00:34:32.320 --> 00:34:34.710
cultivation of thanksgiving

00:34:34.720 --> 00:34:36.710
because I'm telling you, hard days are

00:34:36.710 --> 00:34:36.720
coming—more

00:34:36.720 --> 00:34:39.109
than what any of you

00:34:39.119 --> 00:34:40.710
multi-millionaires will ever think. You think,

00:34:40.720 --> 00:34:41.909
"Well, I've got enough in the bank. I'm

00:34:41.919 --> 00:34:43.109
not going to lose it all."You're going to

00:34:43.119 --> 00:34:45.589
be broke that fast. I've seen it. The

00:34:45.599 --> 00:34:47.349
Lord told me there's going to be a lot

00:34:47.359 --> 00:34:49.750
of you that will be broke within a day.

00:34:49.760 --> 00:34:52.310
In a 24-hour timeframe, you're going to

00:34:52.320 --> 00:34:54.790
lose everything. Remember what I'm

00:34:54.800 --> 00:34:57.030
telling you. You better be hearing the

00:34:57.040 --> 00:34:59.670
voice of God for yourself, listening to

00:34:59.680 --> 00:35:02.710
him on a day-to-day basis. Because if

00:35:02.720 --> 00:35:04.310
you don't, you're going to be in

00:35:04.320 --> 00:35:06.870
trouble. You'll see the last will be

00:35:06.880 --> 00:35:08.150
first and the first will be last, and

00:35:08.160 --> 00:35:10.150
you'll be looking for handouts

00:35:10.160 --> 00:35:11.990
because you weren't thankful and you

00:35:12.000 --> 00:35:13.910
didn't hear God for what's going on and

00:35:13.920 --> 00:35:15.910
what's coming.

00:35:15.920 --> 00:35:18.310
Take time daily at the feet of the

00:35:18.320 --> 00:35:20.550
Father, giving him praise and

00:35:20.560 --> 00:35:22.069
thanksgiving,

00:35:22.079 --> 00:35:24.390
and I'm telling you, you will lack no

00:35:24.400 --> 00:35:27.750
good thing.

00:35:27.760 --> 00:35:30.390
He said, "Beloved, I wish

00:35:30.400 --> 00:35:33.109
above all things that you prosper and be

00:35:33.119 --> 00:35:36.310
in health, even as your soul prospers."But

00:35:36.310 --> 00:35:36.320
there are

00:35:36.320 --> 00:35:37.510
a lot of you who are not

00:35:37.520 --> 00:35:39.910
prosperous even in your souls. You're

00:35:39.920 --> 00:35:41.990
lacking inside; you're lacking in

00:35:42.000 --> 00:35:44.550
relationship with him. My son just told

00:35:44.560 --> 00:35:46.790
me we're at 37 minutes here. I

00:35:50.880 --> 00:35:52.870
hope this message blessed you

00:35:52.880 --> 00:35:56.230
today. Diana and I were talking about

00:35:56.240 --> 00:35:58.069
things; we just get

00:35:58.079 --> 00:35:59.829
caught up.

00:36:06.320 --> 00:36:08.390
Let me pray for you all today. Let's

00:36:08.400 --> 00:36:10.790
agree that all things are possible to

00:36:10.800 --> 00:36:12.230
him that believes. Diana and I are going

00:36:12.240 --> 00:36:14.069
to believe for you—for your miracle,

00:36:14.079 --> 00:36:15.990
for your finances—to believe God for

00:36:16.000 --> 00:36:18.150
everything that you need and that

00:36:18.160 --> 00:36:19.750
nothing is impossible to him who

00:36:19.760 --> 00:36:21.910
believes.

00:36:29.280 --> 00:36:32.310
Father, I just thank you for every

00:36:32.320 --> 00:36:34.550
single person who's watching this

00:36:34.560 --> 00:36:36.550
broadcast.

00:36:36.560 --> 00:36:38.870
I thank you, Father, that

00:36:38.880 --> 00:36:40.630
every single one of them is the head

00:36:40.640 --> 00:36:42.150
and not the tail, and above and not

00:36:42.160 --> 00:36:44.950
beneath. I thank you, Father, that no

00:36:44.960 --> 00:36:47.190
weapon formed against them is going to

00:36:47.200 --> 00:36:49.349
prosper. We thank you, Lord, that we

00:36:49.359 --> 00:36:51.510
have authority over the devil and

00:36:51.520 --> 00:36:54.790
we take our seat. We are grateful and

00:36:54.800 --> 00:36:57.190
thankful for everything that you

00:36:57.200 --> 00:37:00.230
provided for us. Lord, we give you the

00:37:00.240 --> 00:37:02.870
glory and all the honor.

00:37:02.880 --> 00:37:05.270
We just say, "God, we want to take the

00:37:05.280 --> 00:37:08.790
time to thank you for all that

00:37:08.790 --> 00:37:08.800
you've

00:37:08.800 --> 00:37:12.230
provided for us."Thank you, God, for

00:37:12.240 --> 00:37:14.710
all the money, for the food, for

00:37:14.720 --> 00:37:17.190
whatever you've given us. Even

00:37:17.200 --> 00:37:20.230
if it's just five dollars, we want to be grateful.

00:37:20.240 --> 00:37:22.230
Even if it's a hundred dollars, we are grateful.

00:37:22.240 --> 00:37:23.750
Even for the millionaire that's

00:37:23.760 --> 00:37:25.990
watching, be grateful.

00:37:26.000 --> 00:37:28.390
Thank you, Lord, for

00:37:28.390 --> 00:37:28.400
how

00:37:28.400 --> 00:37:30.550
you've taken care of us. Thank you, God,

00:37:30.560 --> 00:37:32.550
for how much you've provided. Thank you,

00:37:32.560 --> 00:37:34.790
Lord, for our electricity, water, gas,

00:37:34.800 --> 00:37:37.670
food, car payments, insurance

00:37:37.670 --> 00:37:37.680
payments—whatever

00:37:37.680 --> 00:37:39.829
it may be. Lord, we want to

00:37:39.839 --> 00:37:41.430
give you praise. Thank you for the

00:37:41.440 --> 00:37:43.670
air that we breathe, for

00:37:43.680 --> 00:37:45.910
the sun that shines in the day, and for

00:37:45.920 --> 00:37:48.150
the moon that shines at night. Thank

00:37:48.160 --> 00:37:49.990
you, Father, for the cold air and for

00:37:50.000 --> 00:37:52.710
the hot sun, for the beautiful fall

00:37:52.720 --> 00:37:54.870
and the beautiful summer, springs, and all

00:37:54.880 --> 00:37:56.390
the beautiful things that you provided

00:37:56.400 --> 00:37:58.710
for us on this earth.

00:37:58.720 --> 00:38:00.470
We thank you, Father, for our children.

00:38:00.470 --> 00:38:00.480
There

00:38:00.480 --> 00:38:01.750
are

00:38:01.760 --> 00:38:03.270
some people that

00:38:03.280 --> 00:38:04.710
can't have them. We thank you, Lord, that the

00:38:04.720 --> 00:38:06.069
people that can't have children in the

00:38:06.079 --> 00:38:08.710
natural will have children—that you

00:38:08.720 --> 00:38:10.790
will provide beautiful children for

00:38:10.800 --> 00:38:13.030
them.

00:38:13.040 --> 00:38:15.750
Thank you, Father, for all that

00:38:15.760 --> 00:38:17.510
you provided in healing and wholeness

00:38:17.520 --> 00:38:20.390
and wellness. They may

00:38:20.400 --> 00:38:22.470
have arthritis or be overcoming

00:38:22.480 --> 00:38:24.230
diabetes, but

00:38:24.240 --> 00:38:25.430
Father, there's something they can be

00:38:25.440 --> 00:38:28.230
thankful for. Thank you, Lord, that

00:38:28.230 --> 00:38:28.240
their

00:38:28.240 --> 00:38:30.230
big toe

00:38:30.240 --> 00:38:32.710
doesn't

00:38:32.720 --> 00:38:35.430
hurt. Thank you, Lord, for the

00:38:35.440 --> 00:38:37.589
elbow that doesn't hurt. Thank you, Lord,

00:38:37.599 --> 00:38:39.910
for the fingers. That's what you have to

00:38:39.920 --> 00:38:42.470
do.

00:38:42.480 --> 00:38:45.510
Thank you, Father; you've

00:38:45.520 --> 00:38:48.950
been so good to us. Regardless of

00:38:48.960 --> 00:38:51.829
whatever it is, God, I thank you.

00:38:51.839 --> 00:38:53.270
Thank you, Lord, for healing in

00:38:53.280 --> 00:38:55.190
everyone's body that's believing: for

00:38:55.200 --> 00:38:58.150
new stomachs, new gallbladders,

00:38:58.160 --> 00:39:00.950
new intestines—whatever they may

00:39:00.960 --> 00:39:03.030
need. Thank you, Father, for all that

00:39:03.040 --> 00:39:05.349
you've provided. Lord, thank you that we

00:39:05.359 --> 00:39:07.349
have the mind of Christ according to

00:39:07.349 --> 00:39:07.359
Second

00:39:07.359 --> 00:39:09.829
Timothy 1:7. God has not given us a

00:39:09.839 --> 00:39:11.670
spirit of fear, but of power, love, and

00:39:11.680 --> 00:39:14.390
of a sound mind.

00:39:14.400 --> 00:39:16.470
We give you praise and

00:39:16.480 --> 00:39:18.150
glory and honor for all that you've done

00:39:18.160 --> 00:39:20.150
and all that you're going to do. As we go

00:39:20.160 --> 00:39:23.109
into the fall months, you say,

00:39:23.119 --> 00:39:25.910
"I've never seen the righteous forsaken

00:39:25.920 --> 00:39:29.349
or his seed begging

00:39:29.349 --> 00:39:29.359
bread."We

00:39:29.359 --> 00:39:31.589
will never be begging bread because

00:39:31.599 --> 00:39:34.470
you always will provide for yours. Lord,

00:39:34.480 --> 00:39:36.710
we give you praise and glory and honor

00:39:36.720 --> 00:39:38.310
for all that you've done and all that

00:39:38.320 --> 00:39:41.430
you continue to do.

00:39:41.440 --> 00:39:43.750
In

00:39:43.760 --> 00:39:45.589
Jesus'name,

00:39:45.599 --> 00:39:47.349
amen.

00:39:47.359 --> 00:39:49.349
Well, we just want to say thank you all

00:39:49.359 --> 00:39:51.270
for joining us today. I hope this

00:39:51.280 --> 00:39:52.790
blessed you.

00:39:52.800 --> 00:39:55.030
It was on my heart

00:39:55.040 --> 00:39:57.109
after what we heard at church to come

00:39:57.119 --> 00:39:59.109
on and tell you all

00:39:59.109 --> 00:39:59.119
this—they're

00:39:59.119 --> 00:40:00.550
right. We've got to live a

00:40:00.560 --> 00:40:01.750
thankful life.

00:40:01.750 --> 00:40:01.760
You've

00:40:01.760 --> 00:40:04.150
got to live a praise-filled life,

00:40:04.160 --> 00:40:05.670
giving God praise for

00:40:05.680 --> 00:40:06.790
everything you have because it's

00:40:06.800 --> 00:40:07.670
important.

00:40:52.560 --> 00:40:54.630
Put a smile on your face and a

00:40:54.640 --> 00:40:57.190
song in your heart. Jesus loves you so

00:40:57.200 --> 00:40:59.030
much and we love you. We will see you

00:40:59.040 --> 00:41:01.030
all next time. God bless you all and I

00:41:01.040 --> 00:41:02.550
hope y'all have a wonderful day.

